3. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper's use of optimization techniques to solve the pose estimation problem may fall under the umbrella of machine learning. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper's use of optimization techniques and its focus on solving a fundamental problem in computer vision may also fall under the broader category of artificial intelligence.
